---
import MainLayout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import TedaviDoktorlari from '../../../components/TedaviDoktorlari.astro'; 

// SEO Title and Description
const pageTitle = "Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery | Wisdom Tooth Extraction | Yuceler A+ Clinic";
const pageDescription = "Expert oral and maxillofacial surgery treatments in Silivri and Catalca. Painless impacted wisdom tooth extraction, cyst operations, sinus lifting, and bone graft applications.";
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle}>
  
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/images/cene-cerrahisi-banner.webp');"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-klinik-koyu/95 via-klinik-koyu/60 to-transparent z-0"></div> 
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block bg-klinik-yesil text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Expert and Reliable</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight text-white drop-shadow-2xl">
          Advanced Technology <br/><span class="text-klinik-yesil">Maxillofacial Surgery</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed drop-shadow-lg">
          All operations such as impacted wisdom teeth, jaw cysts, and advanced implant surgery are performed painlessly and comfortably by our expert physicians accompanied by 3D Tomography.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-start">
        
        <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">What is Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery is the specialty branch that covers the diagnosis and surgical treatment of all kinds of diseases, cysts, and tumors of all soft tissues (gums, palate, tongue, etc.) and hard tissues (teeth, jawbones) in the mouth. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Not only tooth extraction; increasing the bone tissue that is insufficient for implant treatments (bone graft), elevating the sinus cavities (sinus lifting), and jaw joint disorders are also the expertise of this department. All procedures are performed under <strong>maximum sterilization</strong> and completely painlessly.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-klinik-yesil mb-10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Surgical Procedures Performed in Our Clinic</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 font-medium">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Impacted Tooth Operations:</strong> Extraction of wisdom teeth and canine teeth embedded in the jawbone.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Apical Resection:</strong> Surgical cleaning and saving of the root tips of teeth with cysts formed at the root tip.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Sinus Lifting & Bone Graft:</strong> Increasing the volume of the jawbone, which is insufficient for the implant, by adding bone powder.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Cyst and Tumor Surgery:</strong> Removal of cysts formed in the jawbones or soft tissues with pathological examination.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">Surgical Operation Process</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Millimetric Diagnosis with 3D Tomography</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Before every surgical procedure, your jaw structure is examined in 3D with the 3D Volumetric Tomography devices in our clinics. The locations of nerves and vessels are determined millimetrically, and the operation is planned with zero errors.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Painless Surgical Intervention</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">The procedure is performed completely painlessly by our expert maxillofacial surgeons accompanied by strong local anesthetics. We also have a sedation (sleep state) option for our patients with extreme fear.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Healing and Control</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Post-operative swelling/pain is minimized with the medications prescribed by our doctor and the ice compress you will apply. Your healing process is usually completed by removing your stitches after 1 week.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 sticky top-32">
          <img src="/images/cene-cerrahisi-kutu.webp" alt="3D Tomography and Maxillofacial Surgery" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-t-2xl shadow-sm" />
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-8 rounded-b-2xl shadow-xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">You Are Safe With Expert Surgeons</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6 text-sm">Book a free 3D Tomography and expert examination appointment for your impacted wisdom tooth extraction or other surgical procedures.</p>
            
            <a href="https://wa.me/902124000013" target="_blank" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12.031 21.033c-1.56 0-3.084-.42-4.42-1.216l-.317-.189-3.284.861.876-3.203-.207-.331a9.022 9.022 0 0 1-1.378-4.755C3.301 7.155 7.215 3.24 12.031 3.24c2.33 0 4.519.907 6.166 2.555 1.648 1.648 2.556 3.837 2.556 6.167 0 4.914-3.915 8.829-8.73 8.829z" /></svg>
              Contact via WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+902124000013" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-klinik-koyu text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-black transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
              Call Clinic: +90 212 400 00 13
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TedaviDoktorlari tedavi="cene-cerrahisi" />

  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 pb-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Frequently Asked <span class="text-klinik-yesil">Questions</span></h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Things you might wonder about maxillofacial surgery and wisdom tooth extractions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Do wisdom teeth absolutely need to be extracted?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">If there is enough space in the jaw arch and the tooth has erupted healthily, it does not need to be extracted. However, if there is no space in the jaw, if it remains fully or partially impacted, if it causes pain, abscess, and crowding by pushing the teeth in front, it must be surgically extracted.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Are maxillofacial surgery operations painful?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">No. All surgical procedures are performed by our expert physicians by completely numbing the area to be treated (local anesthesia). You will not feel any pain or ache during the operation; there may only be a sensation of touch and pressure.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            What is sinus lifting and bone grafting?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">When an implant is planned for the upper jaw posterior regions, the anatomical sinus cavities in that area may have sagged downwards. In order to provide sufficient bone volume for the implant to be placed, the sinus membrane is surgically pushed upwards, and bone graft is added to the formed space to create a new and solid bone tissue.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-klinik-koyu text-white py-12 border-t-4 border-klinik-turuncu mt-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-klinik-turuncu font-bold text-lg mb-3">Legal Notice</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          This website has been prepared solely for the purpose of informing patients, in full compliance with the Ministry of Health regulations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-left md:text-right">
        <p class="mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Dental Implant Clinic A Plus</p>
        <p class="mb-1">Call Center: <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">+90 212 400 00 13</span></p>
        <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg inline-block text-left border border-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-1 text-xs">Last Updated: <span class="text-white font-bold">21.02.2026</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs">Editor: <a href="mailto:info@dentalimplanttrakya.com" class="text-klinik-turuncu hover:underline">info@dentalimplanttrakya.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <div class="h-16 md:hidden block"></div>

</MainLayout>